    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and strictly following every single maintenance check. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
